      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Hi! I’m Bea, the AI voice interface for Ubie’s Smart Support. I’m designed to streamline patient access and clinical workflows for providers ranging from local clinics to major health systems. To show you how I handle high-volume intake, I’d love to walk you through a brief simulation where you pretend to be a patient calling and I act as an intake coordinator. \n\nShall we begin?"
